data.description: Being sold AS IS -- Uncover the hidden potential of this spacious 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom house that's ready for your personal touch and creative vision. Nestled in a charming neighborhood, this home offers a unique opportunity to customize and create your dream space. Five bedrooms provide endless possibilities - transform them into cozy bedrooms, a home office, a fitness room, or any other space that suits your needs. The two full bathrooms are a solid foundation for renovation, allowing you to craft your own spa-like retreats. The generous backyard is a fantastic space for outdoor activities and entertainment. With a little landscaping, it can become your personal oasis. This property also includes a two-car attached garage. This is your chance to make a house your very own home. Bring your vision, creativity, and a little TLC to unlock the immense potential of this property. Don't miss this opportunity to create the perfect space in an ideal location. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and start the journey of transforming this house into your dream home.
